column21: Any comments about Winslow Dining food?
Idk about Winslow but can chic fil a do breakfast?☹️
I don’t eat there very frequently. I’m picky with my food and like very strongly flavored things. I manage to cook for myself most meals.

As someone who worked the grill, salads, pizza, and deli, it's not supposed to taste the best, it's supposed to be plentiful and last over 10000 kids. If you want health, then go to catering on the right side.
I really like eating at winslow. I just wish that, as a pescatarian (Vegetarian + seafood), they offered more seafood options.
